description:
Ram Kumar’s abstract forms are rooted in emotion, memory, and his journey as one of India’s foremost modernists. They offer a canvas not just to look, but to feel and imagine. This label-making workshop invites you to bridge the distance between artwork and viewer, fostering a personal dialogue with his art.

Come and uncover the layered meanings within abstraction. Join us for a journey of observation, reflection and creative expression.

&nbsp;
